WEBVTT

00:05.170 --> 00:10.610
From master animator Miyazaki, one of the most influential filmmakers of all time,...

00:10.845 --> 00:13.680
...comes a groundbreaking motion picture event.

00:18.480 --> 00:21.520
In a time when gods walked the Earth,...

00:21.855 --> 00:23.850
...an epic battle rages...

00:23.990 --> 00:29.030
...between the encroaching civilization of man and the gods of the forest.

00:29.395 --> 00:31.825
When the forest has been cleared and the wolves wiped out,...

00:31.925 --> 00:34.070
...this place will be the richest land in the world.

00:35.935 --> 00:40.210
It's a war which threatens to unbalance the forces of nature.

00:40.370 --> 00:43.260
It will be a battle the humans will never forget.

00:43.410 --> 00:48.640
Now, the fate of the world rests on the courage of one fearless princess.

00:48.740 --> 00:50.085
I'm not afraid to die.

00:50.280 --> 00:52.520
And I would do anything to get the humans out of here.

00:52.685 --> 00:54.720
And one brave warrior.

00:56.020 --> 00:58.690
You fight like a demon, boy, like something possessed.

00:58.890 --> 01:00.395
What exactly are you here for?

01:00.595 --> 01:03.175
To see with eyes unclouded by hate.

01:03.395 --> 01:07.165
Now, watch closely everyone. I'm going to show you how to kill a god.

01:07.820 --> 01:08.235
Fire!

01:28.220 --> 01:30.020
You cannot alter your fate.

01:30.190 --> 01:33.725
However, you can rise to meet it if you choose.

01:36.495 --> 01:40.735
Featuring the voices of Gillian Anderson, Billy Crudup,...

01:41.165 --> 01:47.000
...Claire Danes, Minnie Driver, Jada Pinkett-Smith, and Billy Bob Thornton.

01:53.780 --> 01:55.445
Princess Mononoke.

